{"tid":978841,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"J2東京綠茵挖角港隊主帥Gary White後 再挖角香港菁英發展教練","createTime":"2019-01-12T08:31:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-12T13:05:35.000Z","uid":9030,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a4af711cdc7ea0f90ea31d8266b8d062f756539c","tid":978841,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T08:31:43.000Z","msg":"Michael BORIS:<br />\nOf course I am very happy to be working for Tokyo Verdy in the new season. Many thanks <br />\nto manager Gary White who gives me the confidence and the opportunity to work as his <br />\nassistant in a traditional club like Tokyo Verdy.Together with the coaching team and the <br />\nteam, I will do everything I can to ensure that we all have a successful season in our <br />\nanniversary year.Therefore I hope very much for the great support of our fans.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.verdy.co.jp/news/7582\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.verdy.co.jp%2Fnews%2F7582&d=b8z1wYmQJIBDRJKllPC09%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=8981e381\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.verdy.co.jp/news/7582</a>"},{"pid":"891ed0752ef959667fe7de3755f6a26769a50d89","tid":978841,"uid":9030,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T08:36:39.000Z","msg":"保域斯(Michael BORIS) 11月30日上任香港菁英發展教練，但僅一周已極速離任，省港盃主帥郭嘉諾早前透露保域斯因不適應香港氣侯辭職，結果今日J2東京綠茵公佈保域斯將擔任該隊教練。"},{"pid":"cd7360d66f5e43544faf691e26ce3c792e6d0d1e","tid":978841,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T08:38:13.000Z","msg":"12月11日加利韋特請辭 加盟J2東京綠茵"},{"pid":"925561a91d5de0502d5d13df3346f023c26ce6f8","tid":978841,"uid":28155,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T08:47:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港足球<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ba3dc71cb51c768472403a13cb5054fb775e116","tid":978841,"uid":9030,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedB